## Yabai

alt - h : yabai -m window --focus west
alt - l : yabai -m window --focus east
alt - k : yabai -m window --focus north
alt - j : yabai -m window --focus south
shift + alt - h : yabai -m window --swap west
shift + alt - l : yabai -m window --swap east
shift + alt - k : yabai -m window --swap north
shift + alt - j : yabai -m window --swap south
ctrl + alt - h : yabai -m window --warp west
ctrl + alt - l : yabai -m window --warp east
ctrl + alt - k : yabai -m window --warp north
ctrl + alt - j : yabai -m window --warp south

alt - s : yabai -m display --focus west
alt - g : yabai -m display --focus east
ctrl + alt - s : yabai -m window --display west; yabai -m display --focus west
ctrl + alt - g : yabai -m window --display east; yabai -m display --focus east

shift + alt - r : yabai -m space --rotate 270
shift + alt - y : yabai -m space --mirror y-axis
shift + alt - x : yabai -m space --mirror x-axis

shift + alt - t : yabai -m window --toggle float --grid 4:4:1:1:2:2
alt - f : yabai -m window --toggle zoom-fullscreen
alt - e : yabai -m space --balance

# Increase Window Size
ctrl + alt - u : yabai -m window --resize bottom:0:20
 ctrl + alt - y : yabai -m window --resize left:-20:0
 ctrl + alt - i : yabai -m window --resize top:0:-20
 ctrl + alt - o : yabai -m window --resize right:20:0

# Decrease Window Size
 alt + shift - y : yabai -m window --resize right:-20:0
 alt + shift - u : yabai -m window --resize top:0:20
 alt + shift - i : yabai -m window --resize bottom:0:-20
 alt + shift - o : yabai -m window --resize left:20:0


shift + alt - p : yabai -m window --space prev
shift + alt - n : yabai -m window --space next

ctrl + alt - 0 : yabai -m window --space 0
ctrl + alt - 1 : yabai -m window --space 1
ctrl + alt - 2 : yabai -m window --space 2
ctrl + alt - 3 : yabai -m window --space 3
ctrl + alt - 4 : yabai -m window --space 4
ctrl + alt - 5 : yabai -m window --space 5
ctrl + alt - 6 : yabai -m window --space 6
ctrl + alt - 7 : yabai -m window --space 7
ctrl + alt - 8 : yabai -m window --space 8
ctrl + alt - 9 : yabai -m window --space 9

shift + ctrl + alt - n : yabai -m config top_padding 24
shift + ctrl + alt - m : yabai -m config top_padding 50

## Applications

